---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import {Image} from "astro:assets"
---

<Layout title="JavaZone 2024 Partner">

    <main>
        <article>
            <h1>JavaZone 2024 Partner</h1>

            <section>
                <h2>Partner registration</h2>
                <p>Partner registration opens <b>January 15th 2024 at 10:00</b></p>

                <p><a target="_blank" href="https://app.checkin.no/event/65953/javazone-2024-partnership">Follow this
                    link to register</a>. (This will send you to Checkin)</p>
                <p>There are three options to choose from, standard, restaurant and concept stand, where the two latter
                    includes increased space to showcase yourself. See below for more details on the different
                    packages.</p>
                <p>All partner packages are sold first come first served starting January 15th and as long as there are
                    still packages left. If an option is sold out, you can register on a waiting list in case there are
                    any cancellations</p>
                <p>You must choose one type of package. Once you complete the registration you will receive a
                    confirmation of your choice. The formal contract and invoice will be sent to you later </p>
                <p>
                <p>
                    <a target="_blank" class="button-style"
                       href="https://app.checkin.no/event/65953/javazone-2024-partnership">Register here</a>
                </p>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2>Partner packages</h2>
                <p>If you have any questions, please send us an e-mail at <a href="mailto:partner@java.no">partner@java.no</a>
                </p>
                <div class="packages">
                    <section class="package">
                        <h3>Standard package</h3>
                        <div>
                            <p class="bold">Price</p>
                            <p>95 000,- NOK ex VAT</p>
                        </div>
                        <Image class="stand-image" alt="hello" src="/images/standard-stand.png" width="800"
                               height="450"/>
                        <p class="bold">Stand</p>
                        <p>6 square meters (3x2) with back and side wall, in the main conference hall.</p>

                        <p class="bold">Profiling</p>
                        <p>Logo with link on homepage and profiling in Oslo Spectrum</p>
                        <p class="bold">Stand ticket</p>
                        <p>4 flexible tickets for stand personnel.</p>
                        <p class="bold">Particiant tickets</p>
                        <p>Partner price on tickets for your colleagues</p>

                    </section>
                    <section class="package">
                        <h3>Concept stand</h3>
                        <div>
                            <p class="bold">Additional price</p>
                            <p>78 000,- NOK ex VAT</p>
                        </div>
                        <Image class="stand-image" alt="hello" src="/images/concept-stand.png" width="800"
                               height="450"/>
                        <p>All the benefits of the standard package.</p>
                        <p>Stand of 48 square meters (8X6 m)</p>
                        <p>Large space for showing off your own concept</p>
                        <p>Extremely limited â€“ only <span class="bold">2</span> available</p>

                    </section>
                    <section class="package">
                        <h3>Restaurant stand</h3>
                        <div>
                            <p class="bold">Additional price</p>
                            <p>85 000,- NOK ex VAT</p>
                        </div>
                        <Image class="stand-image" alt="hello" src="/images/restaurant-stand.png" width="800"
                               height="450"/>

                        <p>All the benefits of the standard package with a restaurant stand</p>
                        <p>24 square meters (6x4 m) with a connected restaurant</p>
                        <p> Continuous food serving from your stand throughout the conference.</p>
                        <p>Menu in cooperation with event partners.</p>
                    </section>
                    <section class="package partner-tickets">
                        <h3>Partner tickets</h3>
                        <p>Order from March 1st until May 15th</p>
                        <p>Round robin distribution on tickets ordered by May 15th</p>
                        <p>First come first served if tickets are still left after May 15th</p>
                        <div>
                            <p class="bold">Additional price</p>
                            <p>7 990,- NOK ex VAT</p>
                        </div>
                    </section>
                </div>
            </section>
            <section>
                <h2>Partner meeting #1 (December 5th 2023)</h2>
                <div style="position:relative;">
                    <iframe title="JavaZone 2024 partner meeting video"
                            src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/891500045?h=7df20a26e4" width="640" height="360"
                            frameborder="0" allow="autoplay; fullscreen; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen></iframe>
                    <p><a href="https://vimeo.com/891500045">JavaZone 2024 Partner Meeting #1</a> from <a
                        href="https://vimeo.com/user125589327">Macsimum AS</a> on <a href="https://vimeo.com">Vimeo</a>.
                    </p></div>
                <script is:inline src="https://player.vimeo.com/api/player.js"></script>
                <p><a
                    href="https://www.dropbox.com/scl/fi/wivcmqsj9a5058p8s3qcj/JZ2024PartnermeetingOne.pdf?rlkey=48d1t09xcfjqts9kfytk7aegb&dl=0">Slides
                    from the partner meeting</a>
                </p>
            </section>

        </article>
    </main>
</Layout>

<style>
    body {
        background: wheat;
        color: black;
    }

    main {
        margin: 2rem;
    }


    h1 {
        font-size: 3rem;
    }

    h2 {
        font-size: 2rem;
    }

    h3 {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
    }

    p {
        word-wrap: break-word;

        line-height: 1.6rem;
    }

    section {
        padding: 1rem;
    }

    .package {
        margin: 1rem 0;
        background: blanchedalmond;
        border-radius: 16px;
    }

    @media screen and (min-width: 1400px) {
        .packages {
            display: grid;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            margin: 1rem 0;
        }

        .package {
            gap: 1rem;
            margin: 0;
            display: grid;
            align-content: baseline;
        }
    }

    .bold {
        font-weight: bold;
    }

    .partner-tickets {
        grid-column: 1 / end;
    }

    .stand-image {
        object-fit: cover;
    }
</style>
